258. Add Digits

Example 1:
Input: num = 38
Output: 2
Explanation: The process is
38 --> 3 + 8 --> 11
11 --> 1 + 1 --> 2 
Since 2 has only one digit, return it.

Example 2:
Input: num = 0
Output: 0


SOLUTION:

class Solution {
    public int addDigits(int num) {
        if(num<10){
            return num;
        }
        int s=0;
        while(num!=0){
            int d=num%10;
            s+=d;
            num/=10;
        }
        return addDigits(s);
    }
}
